Good morning! Have a good day.
To get started, you need to create an account on our platform. This involves providing your basic information and details about your cleaning requirements.
Once you have created an account, you can start searching for maids who meet your specific needs. You can browse through profiles, read reviews, and check availability to find the right match.
On the day of your appointment, your maid will arrive at your home ready to clean. You can relax and enjoy your clean home, knowing that your maid has been vetted and is trustworthy.
Payment for the services is usually made through the app, either upfront or after the service. You can manage your payments and review past appointments through your account dashboard.

Welcome to our website, where we strive to make the process of hiring maids as simple and stress-free as possible. Our mission is to connect households with reliable and trustworthy domestic help, allowing busy homeowners to focus on the things that matter most to them.

We understand that finding the right maid can be a daunting task, which is why we have developed an easy-to-use platform that streamlines the process. With just a few clicks, our users can search for maids based on their specific needs and preferences, book appointments, and communicate with their maid through our secure messaging system.

We are committed to providing our users with the highest quality service possible, which is why we thoroughly vet all of the maids on our platform. Our team conducts extensive background checks, reference checks, and interviews to ensure that every maid we work with is trustworthy, reliable, and skilled.

We also believe in transparency and accountability, which is why we provide our users with the tools they need to easily manage their maid appointments and payments. Our users can access their account information, review past appointments, and leave feedback for their maid all in one convenient location.

Our goal on our website is to become the go-to platform for households seeking reliable and trustworthy maids. We aim to continually improve our platform to make it more user-friendly and efficient, allowing our users to easily book appointments, communicate with their maids, and manage their accounts.
Phone number must be of 11 digits excluding 0
